WEBVTT

00:00:00.336 --> 00:00:02.636
♪♪♪

00:00:01.467 --> 00:00:03.560
(INDISTINCT CHATTERS)

00:00:17.329 --> 00:00:19.961
- JODIE: I feel like
everyone is looking at us.

00:00:20.042 --> 00:00:23.152
- RYAN: That's not just the feeling.
Everyone <i>is</i> looking at us.

00:00:32.492 --> 00:00:34.535
- JODIE: This dress sucks.

00:00:34.862 --> 00:00:37.462
I knew I should've worn something else.

00:00:37.362 --> 00:00:39.042
- RYAN: Dress is perfect.

00:00:40.005 --> 00:00:41.205
You look great.

00:00:42.978 --> 00:00:44.778
But the most important thing...

00:00:45.115 --> 00:00:46.635
Act natural.

00:00:46.765 --> 00:00:49.596
If anyone speaks to you, just smile.

00:00:49.814 --> 00:00:53.697
- JODIE: So do you want me to act natural
or do you want me to smile?

00:00:53.151 --> 00:00:56.508
- RYAN: (CHUCKLES)
I didn't know you have a sense of humour.

00:00:56.561 --> 00:00:58.694
- JODIE: Only when I'm scared to death.

00:00:58.414 --> 00:01:01.153
- MAN: Ryan. I'm delighted
you could attend.

00:01:00.940 --> 00:01:03.583
- RYAN: Oh, it's a pleasure, Sheik Ahmad.

00:01:03.837 --> 00:01:07.229
I, uh, would like you
to meet my assistant, Elizabeth.

00:01:07.269 --> 00:01:13.148
- AHMAD: I was unaware that American diplomacy
was undertaken such disarming charm.

00:01:13.303 --> 00:01:15.437
The pleasure is mine, Elizabeth.

00:01:16.065 --> 00:01:18.917
- RYAN: Gentlemen,
I give you back your host.

00:01:19.048 --> 00:01:20.728
We'll talk later, Ahmad.

00:01:20.632 --> 00:01:22.365
- AHMAD: Until then, Ryan.

00:01:27.392 --> 00:01:28.992
- RYAN: He hates me.

00:01:28.562 --> 00:01:31.402
The whole time he's imagining
my head on a stick.

00:01:31.255 --> 00:01:32.815
I think he found you charming.

00:01:32.842 --> 00:01:34.909
- JODIE: I should be flattered.

00:01:35.510 --> 00:01:38.893
- RYAN: I'm gonna shake some hands.
Blend in and find somewhere quiet.

00:01:38.814 --> 00:01:40.747
You know what you have to do.

00:01:42.185 --> 00:01:43.585
Ambassador!

00:01:43.612 --> 00:01:45.612
You're a sight for sore eyes.

00:01:48.050 --> 00:01:50.584
- JODIE: I need to find a quiet place.

00:01:58.506 --> 00:01:59.546
(MUSIC STOPS)

00:02:10.470 --> 00:02:14.295
♪♪♪

00:02:36.889 --> 00:03:00.320
- WOMAN: (SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:03:17.128 --> 00:03:19.694
- JODIE: Aiden. Aiden, are you ready?

00:03:19.451 --> 00:03:20.811
(AIDEN RESPONDS)

00:03:20.993 --> 00:03:23.843
There's a large painting
in one of the rooms upstairs.

00:03:23.883 --> 00:03:25.483
Behind it is a safe.

00:03:25.796 --> 00:03:28.596
The documents we're looking for
are inside.

00:03:28.975 --> 00:03:32.438
But there're guards and cameras
so you have to be careful, you got it?

00:03:32.279 --> 00:03:34.349
(AIDEN RESPONDS)

00:03:46.552 --> 00:03:47.552
<i>Hurry Aiden!</i>

00:03:50.260 --> 00:03:53.126
<i>It hurts like hell
when you're too far away.</i>

00:04:11.302 --> 00:04:13.969
<i>An office, with a portrait of the Sheik.</i>

00:04:15.221 --> 00:04:16.661
<i>This is the place.</i>

00:04:22.317 --> 00:04:23.317
<i>Crap.</i>

00:04:23.630 --> 00:04:25.963
<i>You gotta distract the guard first.</i>

00:04:37.173 --> 00:04:39.106
- GUARD: (SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:04:43.866 --> 00:04:44.986
- JODIE: <i>Okay.</i>

00:04:45.313 --> 00:04:48.046
<i>Nobody would monitor the main office now.</i>

00:04:47.854 --> 00:04:49.294
<i>We should be safe.</i>

00:05:06.248 --> 00:05:08.648
<i>There's gotta be a switch somewhere.</i>

00:05:09.453 --> 00:05:11.133
<i>To move the painting.</i>

00:05:12.258 --> 00:05:13.458
<i>Find it, Aiden.</i>

00:05:25.674 --> 00:05:28.074
<i>Now it's safe, we can open the safe.</i>

00:05:29.444 --> 00:05:30.444
<i>Good job.</i>

00:05:30.894 --> 00:05:32.627
<i>Now we have to read the documents.</i>

00:05:32.668 --> 00:05:33.788
<i>Make it quick.</i>

00:05:34.613 --> 00:05:36.480
<i>I can't hold on much longer.</i>

00:05:36.413 --> 00:05:38.093
<i>Okay, now don't move.</i>

00:06:10.577 --> 00:06:12.510
- GUARD: (SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:06:14.020 --> 00:06:17.104
(SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:06:17.450 --> 00:06:20.023
- WOMAN: (SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:06:20.116 --> 00:06:22.342
(SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:06:22.441 --> 00:06:26.454
(BOTH SPEAKING IN ARABIC)

00:06:43.176 --> 00:06:44.176
- WOMAN: (IN ENGLISH)
Sorry.

00:06:44.748 --> 00:06:47.068
I can't do anything to help you.

00:06:48.623 --> 00:06:49.623
Good luck.

00:07:04.108 --> 00:07:06.674
- JODIE:(PANTING)

00:07:17.604 --> 00:07:21.151
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:07:27.305 --> 00:07:28.705
- RYAN: Jodie, you alright?

00:07:28.265 --> 00:07:29.945
- JODIE: Don't touch me!

00:07:31.741 --> 00:07:32.941
I wanna go now.

00:07:33.298 --> 00:07:35.232
- RYAN: Right, we're leaving.